Class StationConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object
    • dk.aau.cs.giraf.train.StationConfiguration
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable

    public class StationConfiguration
extends java.lang.Object
implements android.os.Parcelable
    This class holds information about a single station. It contains the id of a pictogram used for the category and an array of ids for the associated pictograms.
